name: RUSKI GOING DOWN
description:
"Attention, Ukrainians! This is A Russian Military Ship speaking! If you don't surrender we will attack!"

"Russian Military Ship, go fuck yourself!"

This story already became a meme 

Russians arrived to Ukraine with a strange idea of some pro-ukrainian nationalists occupying the country. This is not the case. We are happy to be independant Ukrainians and we will stay so.

Please support our boys who are taking a heavy load of aggression now and fighting out their. This artwork is created by Ukrainian artist Koleno Golova (Knee Head) to raise money for body armour
